      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "那夜王睡不着覺，就吩咐人取歷史來，念給他聽。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "During that night the king could not sleep so he gave an order to bring the book of records, the chronicles, and they were read before the king."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "That night the king could not sleep; so he ordered the book of the chronicles, the record of his reign, to be brought in and read to him."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "That night the king had trouble sleeping, so he ordered an attendant to bring the book of the history of his reign so it could be read to him."
      }
